{"id":1,"name":"Elder Tala","note":"","pages":[{"conditions":{"actorId":1,"actorValid":false,"itemId":1,"itemValid":false,"selfSwitchCh":"A","selfSwitchValid":false,"switch1Id":2,"switch1Valid":false,"switch2Id":1,"switch2Valid":false,"variableId":1,"variableValid":false,"variableValue":0},"directionFix":false,"image":{"tileId":0,"characterName":"tallcharacters/$People2_1","direction":8,"pattern":1,"characterIndex":0},"list":[{"code":213,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,7,false]},{"code":108,"indent":0,"parameters":["<Icon: 172>"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["Elder",1,0,2,"Elder Tala"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<WordWrap>Ah, you’ve arrived... I feared it might be too late. I summoned you because, I need to tell you something important.."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["Elder",0,0,2,"Elder Tala"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<WordWrap>Our village, Luntian, has always been a peaceful place. "]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["Elder",0,0,2,"Elder Tala"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<WordWrap>Protected by the spirits of the land, we've lived in harmony with nature for generations. But recently... things have changed.."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["Elder",0,0,2,"Elder Tala"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<WordWrap>Some strange things have been happening. Crops are failing, animals are fleeing, and an unsettling feeling hangs over the village..."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["Elder",0,0,2,"Elder Tala"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<WordWrap>People speak of sightings—something unnatural lurking in the forests and mountains.. The air is thick with fear."]},{"code":102,"indent":0,"parameters":[["Do you know what it is?"],-1,0,2,0]},{"code":402,"indent":0,"parameters":[0,"Do you know what it is?"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["Elder",1,0,2,"Elder Tala"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["<WordWrap>Not exactly. But a former elder believe it’s connected to an ancient creature.. a monster, thought to be a myth... the Tikbalang."]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["Elder",0,0,2,"Elder Tala"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["<WordWrap>It is said to play tricks on travelers, leading them astray, but this time, its power seems indistinct, more malevolent."]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["Elder",0,0,2,"Elder Tala"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["<WordWrap>We do not know why the Tikbalang has grown so strong, or what has awakened it from its slumber. "]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["Elder",0,0,2,"Elder Tala"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["<WordWrap>But one thing is clear. its going to wreak havoc not just our village, but the entire land if it is not stopped."]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["Elder",1,0,2,"Elder Tala"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["<WordWrap>You have a special connection to the spirits, young one. That is why I have called for you."]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["Elder",0,0,2,"Elder Tala"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["<WordWrap>You may be our only hope to uncover the truth behind this curse and defeat the Tikbalang before it’s too late"]},{"code":102,"indent":1,"parameters":[["Where do I start?"],-1,0,2,0]},{"code":402,"indent":1,"parameters":[0,"Where do I start?"]},{"code":101,"indent":2,"parameters":["Elder",1,0,2,"Elder Tala"]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["<WordWrap>Start by visiting the sacred shrine in the forest. The Tikbalang is cunning, so be on your guard—its illusions are strong"]},{"code":101,"indent":2,"parameters":["Elder",0,0,2,"Elder Tala"]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["<WordWrap>But with the right preparations, and if you listen to the whispers of the spirits, you may find the path to victory."]},{"code":101,"indent":2,"parameters":["Elder",0,0,2,"Elder Tala"]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["<WordWrap>Before you go, take this. It's a treasure of our village—the Guard Ring. It is crafted by the village’s elders long ago"]},{"code":101,"indent":2,"parameters":["Elder",0,0,2,"Elder Tala"]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["it will protect you from the Tikbalang’s tricks"]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["and give you strength when you need it most."]},{"code":249,"indent":2,"parameters":[{"name":"Item","volume":25,"pitch":70,"pan":-100}]},{"code":101,"indent":2,"parameters":["",0,1,1,""]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["<center>You recieve Guard ring \\I[145]!"]},{"code":128,"indent":2,"parameters":[74,0,0,1,false]},{"code":101,"indent":2,"parameters":["Elder",1,0,2,"Elder Tala"]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["<WordWrap>Also, visit Mang Tani, the blacksmith. He’s been preparing some tools that will be helpful. "]},{"code":101,"indent":2,"parameters":["Elder",1,0,2,"Elder Tala"]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["<WordWrap>His skills will ensure you’re ready to face the Tikbalang. Do not go unprepared, as the path ahead will test you."]},{"code":101,"indent":2,"parameters":["Elder",1,0,2,"Elder Tala"]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["<WordWrap>Now, go. The fate of Luntian rests on your shoulders. May the spirits guide you and keep you safe."]},{"code":123,"indent":2,"parameters":["A",0]},{"code":222,"indent":2,"parameters":[]},{"code":0,"indent":2,"parameters":[]},{"code":404,"indent":1,"parameters":[]},{"code":0,"indent":1,"parameters":[]},{"code":404,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":123,"indent":0,"parameters":["A",0]},{"code":0,"indent":0,"parameters":[]}],"moveFrequency":3,"moveRoute":{"list":[{"code":0,"parameters":[]}],"repeat":true,"skippable":false,"wait":false},"moveSpeed":3,"moveType":0,"priorityType":1,"stepAnime":false,"through":false,"trigger":1,"walkAnime":true},{"conditions":{"actorId":1,"actorValid":false,"itemId":1,"itemValid":false,"selfSwitchCh":"A","selfSwitchValid":true,"switch1Id":21,"switch1Valid":false,"switch2Id":3,"switch2Valid":false,"variableId":1,"variableValid":fals